        - Use Items
        For Items

        With The Item Displayed Large, Select Another Item,

        If
        You Tap The Item Displayed In Large Size, The Item Will Be Added To The Item.

        Can
        Be Used.


        You Can See Hints When You Don''t Understand.


        Let''s
        Investigate Various Places So That We Can Escape.'
